WEBVTT

00:01.346 --> 00:04.593
Daddy is the sweetest daddy in the world.

00:08.421 --> 00:10.885
Daddy is the most handsome.

00:13.277 --> 00:14.669
The most clever.

00:17.323 --> 00:18.489
The kindest.

00:21.255 --> 00:23.205
He is my Superman.

00:26.367 --> 00:29.526
Daddy wants me to do well at school.

00:32.377 --> 00:35.251
Daddy is just great, but...

00:37.209 --> 00:38.315
...he lies.

00:40.853 --> 00:44.365
He lies about having a job.

00:50.979 --> 00:53.930
He lies about having money.

00:56.971 --> 01:00.047
He lies that he's not tired.

01:02.845 --> 01:05.855
He lies that he's not hungry.

